reg_info.full_title: O. Reg. 194/96: CESSATION OF THE APPLICATION OF PART III OF THE MUNICIPAL AFFAIRS ACT TO THE TOWNSHIPS OF GAUTHIER AND MATACHEWAN
reg_info.reg_name_text: CESSATION OF THE APPLICATION OF PART III OF THE MUNICIPAL AFFAIRS ACT TO THE TOWNSHIPS OF GAUTHIER AND MATACHEWAN
reg_info.act_under: Municipal Act   Loi sur les municipalités

content.content: 1. Part III of the Municipal Affairs Act, as made applicable by subsection 358 (5) of the Municipal Act, ceases to apply to The Corporation of the Township of Gauthier and The Corporation of the Township of Matachewan. O. Reg. 194/96, s. 1.
